#

Portokalopita Delight

$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

GlutenEggsDairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-Free

Tags:

DessertCakeSweet

Description

A delightful Greek-inspired orange cake, infused with aromatic spices and a luscious syrup for an unforgettable taste experience.

Ingredients

  • Phyllo dough: 1 package (16 oz)
  • Fresh oranges: 3, zested and juiced
  • Granulated sugar: 1 cup
  • Eggs: 4
  • Plain yogurt: 1 cup
  • Baking powder: 1 tsp
  • Cinnamon: 1 tsp
  • Butter: 1/2 cup, melted
  • Vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • Honey: 1/2 cup
